{"tid":1395671,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"搭開九巴嘅同我入嚟！！！！","createTime":"2019-08-01T23:18:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T07:41:14.000Z","uid":38432,"like":27,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"aa6cc46a3bd0401b18150b075ab1c51844efb9c1","tid":1395671,"uid":38432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T23:18:22.000Z","msg":"<strong>九巴開辦新路線33　連接荃灣西及油塘</strong><br />\n<br />\n為方便乘客便捷地來往荃灣西及油塘，九巴將於2019年7月22日（星期一）起，開辦路線33 [荃灣西站巴士總站&hArr;油塘巴士總站]。新路線主要途經荃灣南、黃大仙、九龍灣及觀塘。乘客由荃灣西前往黃大仙，預計只需約20分鐘（實際行車時間視乎路面情況而定）。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8cbe2360d5477c9953dbe838895877cd9524ed5","tid":1395671,"uid":38432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T23:29:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我無野講。"},{"pid":"8beb797b5913c7e5be3d7ec1cac9746db2dccd7b","tid":1395671,"uid":38432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T00:06:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> I go to school by bus"},{"pid":"6e5751a604e2886a1b9c6e10301190f041fd1012","tid":1395671,"uid":43100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T00:22:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9ed54521e8a5e7640d1b34d2f866dcc5c4e454c","tid":1395671,"uid":38432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T00:29:03.000Z","msg":"香城電台交通消息<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<blockquote>2019-08-02<br />\n<br />\n汀九橋往九龍慢車，影響屯門公路往九龍近汀九車多，龍尾：深井。<br />\n<br />\n2019-08-02 HKT 08:15<br />\n<br />\n較早前獅子山隧道公路往九龍方向，近隔田村慢線交通意外已清理，龍尾：博康邨。<br />\n<br />\n2019-08-02 HKT 08:03<br />\n<br />\n將軍澳隧道將軍澳入口，龍尾：龍尾：茵怡花園。<br />\n<br />\n2019-08-02 HKT 08:01<br />\n<br />\n公主道過海，龍尾：康莊道橋面。<br />\n<br />\n2019-08-02 HKT 07:45<br />\n<br />\n獅子山隧道公路往九龍方向，近隔田村的慢線有交通意外，龍尾：接近博康邨。<br />\n<br />\n2019-08-02 HKT 07:36<br />\n<br />\n較早前屯門公路往九龍方向，近深井的交通意外已清理，一帶車多。<br />\n<br />\n2019-08-02 HKT 07:31<br />\n<br />\n現時各條隧道交通正常。<br />\n<br />\n2019-08-02 HKT 07:15<br />\n<br />\n屯門公路往九龍方向，近深井有交通意外，一帶車多。<br />\n<br />\n2019-08-02 HKT 07:02<br />\n<br />\n北角有水務工程：車身長度超逾5米的車輛不能由英皇道左轉入健康東街。<br />\n<br />\n2019-08-02 HKT 06:50<br />\n<br />\n因強風關係：港珠澳大橋香港連接路及主橋的最高車速限制仍然維持每小時50公里。<br />\n<br />\n2019-08-02 HKT 06:30<br />\n<br />\n新田公路路面重鋪工程：直至06:00，新田公路往落馬洲方向，通往錦繡花園迴旋處的支路封閉，一帶有改道措施，請留意現場指示。<br />\n<br />\n2019-08-02 HKT 00:05<br />\n<br />\n</blockquote>"},{"pid":"7114cb89ea20c65a9e856311e37cd088aa9e76ce","tid":1395671,"uid":43100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T00:49:02.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推"},{"pid":"0bbeb86f51805795d313216d8c3326b6fbc722cf","tid":1395671,"uid":38432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T01:02:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe0a9e29396615ff890eb953df06e480f0171c43","tid":1395671,"uid":38432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T02:05:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有無懶瞓豬唔記得落車返工呀？"},{"pid":"1635ded995c7680bfcac2e6b66f040dc5e931a46","tid":1395671,"uid":43100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T03:58:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f08242e1d9745fb44fdc87abc5a3ae92e90d6cb9","tid":1395671,"uid":71213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T04:18:32.000Z","msg":"仆街㩒錯負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申 九巴車長巴打 歡迎幫部車裝飾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"780621cc8de41c08c090b3e74562aa41c735cf8a","tid":1395671,"uid":38432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f08242e1d9745fb44fdc87abc5a3ae92e90d6cb9","tid":13956